{"tid":46489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[煙鏟末日]煙包忠告擬擴面積至85%","createTime":"2016-12-19T16:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T16:52:24.000Z","uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd660c890459aea955a208b7712c3da6cf3c291","tid":46489,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街第日煙鏟真正買包陽萎返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161219/large/1482149843_3a50.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161219%2Flarge%2F1482149843_3a50.jpg&d=7VTm%2BqeeYZz6%2BOv%2BOZ%2BwxIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=819da564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161219%2Flarge%2F1482149843_3a50.jpg&h=91274d1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161219/large/1482149843_3a50.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161219/56068561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161219%2F56068561&d=7VTm%2BqeeYZz6%2BOv%2BOZ%2BwxIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=c73f375b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161219%2F56068561&h=836a2fe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161219/56068561</a><br />\n 立法會衞生事務委員會開會，討論食物及衞生局提出的煙包上健康忠告建議，包括擬把煙包上健康忠告圖示的覆蓋率，由現時50%加至85%，以進一步增加煙民戒煙意欲。泛民及建制議員均表示支持政府加強控煙工作，但認為當局援引的研究及數據欠缺說服力，質疑新措施不但未能降低吸煙率，反會令「假煙」更猖獗。<br />\n<br />\n除了擴大健康忠告圖示面積，當局亦建議煙包需加入「請為你的下一代戒煙」及「戒煙熱線：1833183」字句。自由黨立法會議員邵家輝認為，由於法例訂明煙草商的商業標籤不能與警示重疊，商標只能進一步縮小，變相更容易被假冒，擔心會有更多「假煙」流通市面。他又斥當局的研究只提供片面數據，例如泰國實行煙包上健康忠告圖示擴至85%後，吸煙率不跌反升；澳洲採類似措施之餘，也要三度增加煙稅合共近25%，才能降低吸煙率，質疑當局的研究不盡不實，建議措施亦流於表面，「（當局）全部人都好似趕收工，好似梁振英咁﹗」。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨黃碧雲則稱，雖然同意控煙工作要加強，但現時港人吸煙率降至10%左右，已較發達國家低，質疑新措施阻嚇力不足，不能進一步降低吸煙率。本身是煙民的「長毛」梁國雄更指，警示面積過大，令煙民更難分辨真煙及假煙，隨時令不法之徒有機可乘；又斥政府有意把煙民及煙草商「妖魔化」，「搞到我哋個個都係罪人」。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局副局長陳肇始重申，當局今年已經透過書面及舉辦公聽會，收集煙草商及其他持份者的意見，又強調警示面積越大，戒煙意欲越大，而當局進行過研究，認為留下15%煙包面積予煙商展示商業標籤「好足夠」。"},{"pid":"18f432fb98cfe6b0c6fa9d3e2d41230e91b14290","tid":46489,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"拎岀黎唔會睇煙盒，吹呀"},{"pid":"e34cced9ca413cef5ff1015c013d120ef06506cf","tid":46489,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"最好再加85%煙稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a0aa46a14c430b47820addf26072e09e4d7a3b","tid":46489,"uid":27708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"轉哂爛腳輸撚死班賭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91699ac3f48f4e1cc5cf2c923515f21ef447f7f2","tid":46489,"uid":36585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好再加85%煙稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如直接禁賣咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6985dd707bbdda66daa18523bbc561edccff13cd","tid":46489,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/72/HKSAR_smoking_warning.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F7%2F72%2FHKSAR_smoking_warning.gif&h=77f68c8b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}